Half Nelson;;82;;91;;R;;Dan Dunne (Ryan Gosling) is a history teacher at a Brooklyn school. Though well-liked by his students and colleagues, he secretly spends his evenings hopping bars and getting high. A female student named Drey (Shareeka Epps) catches him in a drug-induced haze after a basketball game, and the two strike up an unlikely friendship. As Dan struggles with his addiction, he tries to act as a mentor to the girl, whose brother is serving time for dealing drugs.;;Drama;;Ryan Fleck;;2006;;Ryan Gosling,Shareeka Epps,Anthony Mackie,Deborah Rush,Jay O. Sanders,Nicole Vicius,Denis O'Hare,Monique Curnen,Starla Benford,Tina Holmes,Karen Chilton,Collins Pennie;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/half_nelson